data.description: Experience the ultimate retirement lifestyle at Carillon in Plainfield! This two-bedroom, two-bathroom townhome features freshly painted interiors, elegant six-panel doors, crown molding, and upgraded windows, with brand-new flooring in the inviting Living/Dining areas. Plus, take advantage of a generous carpet allowance for the cozy bedrooms.   Don't miss this incredible opportunity! Estate Sale, Sold As-Is.   Carillon's Active Adult Community allows you to live like you are on vacation, offering a plethora of Amenties, Activities & Events! THREE (3) Pools (One indoor)! Bocce Ball, Shuffeboard, Tennis & PickleBall Courts! The Clubhouse has numerous amenities for activities with Billards & Poker Room, Wood & Ceramic Shops & a Huge Theatre which serves as a place for Dances, Shows and More! THREE 9-hole golf courses and even a Restaurant opened during Golf Season. There is always something to do in Carillon Plainfeld!
